trans-unit.source: Specifies reporting levels for an accessibility rule defined by an <xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: 指定所定义的可访问性规则的报告级别<xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref>实例。

trans-unit.source: When using extending a class, member or indexer with a <xref:System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute>, you must define the level of reporting that the verification rule represents by specifying one of the VerificationReportLevel values.
trans-unit.target: 使用扩展类、 成员或具有索引器时<xref:System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute>，必须定义报告通过指定 VerificationReportLevel 值之一，表示验证规则的级别。</xref:System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The verification rule represented by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref> instance is an error.
trans-unit.target: 验证规则由<xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref>实例时出错。

trans-unit.source: The verification rule represented by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref> instance is a guideline.
trans-unit.target: 验证规则由<xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref>实例是一个准则。

trans-unit.source: The verification rule represented by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref> instance is a warning.
trans-unit.target: 验证规则由<xref href="System.Web.UI.VerificationAttribute"></xref>实例是一个警告。
